<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē bāṇatarkkākṣiśaśisaṁkhyāgaṇānvi
<lb n="2" break="no"/>tē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrēṣṭhē māsi dvitīyyāyāṁ śuklapakṣārkkavārakē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
<lb n="3"/>gaṁgamāṁbāmahādēvī kūrmmēśē bhaktisaṁyutā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> prādādācaṁ
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dratārārkkaṁ dīpahastāṁ suśōbhitāṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> kūrmmasyāgrē pradīptyartthaṁ prati
<lb n="5" break="no"/>māmapratiprabhāṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> putrapautrābhivṛddhyartthaṁ narasiṁhyama
<lb n="6" break="no"/>hīpatēḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> makuṭaṁ ratnasaṁyuktaṁ karṇapatradvayānvitaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> A
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ccaprabhābhirāpūrṇammuktāhārasya saptakaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> cōḷimālā<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied> tathā
<lb n="8" break="no"/>pyanyā<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>muktāhāraṁ samujvalaṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> suvarṇnapātramēkaṁ ca Ūrdhvapu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>ṁḍradvayaṁ śubhaṁ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> gaṁgamāṁbākṛtō dharmō vaiṣṇavaiḥ pratipālyatā
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Atratyaiḥ bhagavadbhaktai<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>dharmmapālanakāṁkṣibhiḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śakavarṣaṁbulu
<lb n="11"/>1265 gunnēṁṭi jyēṣṭa śukla dvitīyyayu ravivāramunāṁḍu
<lb n="12"/>gaṁgamahādēviṁgāru tamaku putrapautrābhivṛddhinni Āyu
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṣkāmyārtthasiddhinni pratāpaśrī vīranarasiṁhyadēvamahārāju
<lb n="14" break="no"/>lakunnu dīrghāyuṣmatsuputrāvāptyartthamu rājyābhivṛddhigā
<lb n="15" break="no"/>nu śrīkūrmmanādhuni sannidhini Akhaṁḍḍadīpahastapratimannu na
<lb n="16" break="no"/>varatnāla makuṭamunnu mutyālahārālu 7 pahiṁḍikuḍu
<lb n="17" break="no"/>ka 1 cōḷimāla 1 mutyālahāra 1 cinnālu 2 Ivi samarppiṁci
<lb n="18" break="no"/>ri <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmamu tirupati śrīvaiṣṇavarakṣa <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatruṇāpikṛtōdha
<lb n="19" break="no"/>rmmaḥ pālanīyyō manīṣibhiḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g><note n="434-1">The other half of this well known verse is omitted.</note>
</p>

